| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0621 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhouse)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: d4270baf-d18a-56ff-94fd-c2baeb2da7d5"
